    <main id="main-content" class="container">
        <section class="intro">
            <h2>About This Guide</h2>
            <p>This page lists all the animated, automated <strong>Music Machines</strong> that can be seen and/or heard at the <a href="http://www.houseontherock.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">House on the Rock</a> attraction located on Highway 23 between Dodgeville and Spring Green, WI.</p>
            <p>They are listed in the order they are found in the Tour of the House and other buildings on the grounds. Included are all musical instruments (#1-42), and all non-musical machines (#A-I) which require tokens.</p>
            <div class="note" role="alert">
                <strong>Tokens:</strong> Tokens can be purchased at numerous locations along the Tour at four for $1.00. Quarters cannot be used to play the machines, only tokens. Unused tokens can be redeemed or spent in the Gift Shop at the end of the Tour.
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="tour-section" id="tour1">
            <div class="tour-header">
                <h3>Tour 1 - The Original Experience</h3>
                <p>Includes the Gate House, House on the Rock, and Infinity Room</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tour-content">
                <ol class="machine-list">
                    <li class="machine-item">
                        <div class="machine-name">The Gate House Ensemble</div>
                        <div class="machine-details">
                            <p>Free, plays continuously</p>
                            <div class="token-info">Features: Ravel's "Bolero", Grieg "Concerto", Tchaikovsky "Concerto"</div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="machine-item">
                        <div class="machine-name">The Gallery of the Bells</div>
                        <div class="machine-details">
                            <p>Does not play</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="machine-item">
                        <div class="machine-name">The Moon of Manakoora</div>
                        <div class="machine-details">
                            <p>2 tokens</p>
                            <div class="token-info">Features: "Harbor Lights", "Hello Young Lovers"</div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="machine-item">
                        <div class="machine-name">Baby Grand Piano #3 (1921 A.B. Chase)</div>
                        <div class="machine-details">
                            <p>2 tokens</p>
                            <div class="token-info">Extensive repertoire including "Everybody Loves Somebody", "Let Me Call You Sweetheart", and many more</div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="machine-item">
                        <div class="machine-name">The House Grand Piano</div>
                        <div class="machine-details">
                            <p>Features: "Hungarian Rhapsody No. 2"</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li class="machine-item">
                        <div class="machine-name">Unknown Instrument - "The Godfather"</div>
                        <div class="machine-details">
                            <p>Free, plays continuously</p>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </div>
        </section>

