        <section class="tour-section" id="notes">
            <div class="tour-header">
                <h3>Important Notes</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="tour-content">
                <div class="note" role="alert">
                    <strong>Playable Instruments:</strong> It is unknown exactly which instruments throughout the House are actually being played while you are there, and which have been recorded and are only played through hidden speakers. These music machines are primarily show pieces and are not carefully maintained for ongoing playability.
                </div>
                <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> January 27, 2018</p>
                <p><strong>Source:</strong> Based on the official House on the Rock tour map and personal inventory from October 2006.</p>
